<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFFomenko"><a href="/wiki/Anatoly_Timofeevich_Fomenko" title="Anatoly Timofeevich Fomenko" class="mw-redirect">Fomenko, A. T.</a>. <a href="http://www.univer.omsk.su/foreign/fom/fom.txt" class="external text" title="http://www.univer.omsk.su/foreign/fom/fom.txt" rel="nofollow">"2. Загадочные хроники-дубликаты внутри "учебника скалигера-петавиуса"."</a> (in Russian) (.txt). <i>Новые эмпирико-статистические методики датирования древних событий и приложения к глобальной хронологии древнего и средневекового мира (краткая справка)</i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.univer.omsk.su/foreign/fom/fom.txt" class="external free" title="http://www.univer.omsk.su/foreign/fom/fom.txt" rel="nofollow">http://www.univer.omsk.su/foreign/fom/fom.txt</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-09-12</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=2.+%D0%97%D0%B0%D0%B3%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%BE%D1%87%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B5+%D1%85%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8-%D0%B4%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%BB%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%82%D1%8B+%D0%B2%D0%BD%D1%83%D1%82%D1%80%D0%B8+%22%D1%83%D1%87%D0%B5%D0%B1%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0+%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B8%D0%B3%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B0-%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%B8%D1%83%D1%81%D0%B0%22.&amp;rft.atitle=%D0%9D%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B5+%D1%8D%D0%BC%D0%BF%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%BE-%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%87%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B5+%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8+%D0%B4%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F+%D0%B4%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%B2%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%85+%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%8B%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%B9+%D0%B8+%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B6%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F+%D0%BA+%D0%B3%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B9+%D1%85%D1%80%D0%BE%D